ActAeronautics Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Canadian Aviation Regulations (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisRegulations Amending the CANADIAN AVIATION REGULATIONS (MISCELLANEOUS PROGRAM) in order to (1) correct discrepancies between the French and English versions; (2) harmonize terms used in the regulations with those used in the enabling statute or related regulations; (3) add clarity to regulatory provisions; and (4) update a reference to a manual.
